The paper deals with the specification and verification of a programming language independent controller for multi-level transactions, which involves concurrent updates at different levels of nested locations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-categories.
